FALLBACK: yfinance
  вң“ Graceful degradation if IBKR offline >10 min
  вң“ Free, unlimited calls
  вң“ 2-5s latency
  вң“ No manual intervention needed

AUXILIARY: Polygon (Corporate Actions Only)
  вң“ Dividend calendar (Phase 0 bootstrap, 37.5 min)
